Title: Eye Spy
Plot: When a Navy commander, who was a technical advisor to a civilian contractor for a Navy weapon, is found dead on the beach, the NCIS team investigates the murder using satellite technology.
Writer: George Schenck, Frank Cardea, Dana Coen
GuestStars: Katy Boyer, Bruce Gray, Marguerite MacIntyre, James Morrison, Sean Murray, Victor McCay, Greg Zola, Mercedes Colon, Pancho Demmings, Parry Shen
